      <div class="check"><span class="ck">✓</span><div><h4>Can a screen reader describe your images?</h4><p>Every meaningful image needs a short text description behind it.</p></div></div>
      <div class="check"><span class="ck">✓</span><div><h4>Can someone use it without a mouse?</h4><p>Keyboard-only visitors should be able to reach everything and see where they are.</p></div></div>
      <div class="check"><span class="ck">✓</span><div><h4>Are your forms labeled?</h4><p>Every field should clearly say what it is for, out loud and on screen.</p></div></div>
